Copper Gains as Freeport’s Peru Unit May Strike: LME Preview

-- B y   M a r i a   K o l e s n i k o v a
-- 
2011-09-13T07:10:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-13/copper-gains-as-freeport-s-peru-unit-may-strike-lme-preview.html
Copper advanced for the first time
in three days as workers at Freeport-McMoRan Copper & Gold
Inc.’s Peruvian unit may proceed with a strike tomorrow and as
concerns over financial instability in  Europe  eased amid reports
that  China  may invest in  Italy .  Market News:  Metals News:  
